Package com.vmware.vapi.std.errors

The com.vmware.vapi.std.errors package provides the standard exceptions that can be included in the list of exceptions in the specification of methods to indicate that the method might report those exceptions.

Package com.vmware.vapi.std.errors Description

The com.vmware.vapi.std.errors package provides the standard exceptions that can be included in the list of exceptions in the specification of methods to indicate that the method might report those exceptions. It also provides some classes intended to be used as payload to provide additional information about those exceptions.
